name: Super Ultimate Ultra Grand Mega Rising: Rise of the fallen of the dawn of the creation of the end 64
name_original: Super Ultimate Ultra Grand Mega Rising: Rise of the fallen of the dawn of the creation of the end 64
description: Super Ultimate Ultra Grand Mega Rising: Rise of the fallen of the dawn of the creation of the end 64, a simple top down shooter in which chicken man has the hold of an infinite ammo arsenal and wipes away hordes of enemies until a grand secret is revealed.
